---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Faro Airport Car Rental Guide | TripAxle"
  description="A practical Faro Airport car rental guide for travelers planning Algarve trips, including pickup, returns, and common rental issues."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Faro Airport car rental</p>
    <h1>Faro Airport Car Rental Guide</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Use this page to understand pickup logistics, return considerations, and common
      rental issues at Faro Airport before you reserve.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="top-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Quick airport summary</h2>
      <p>
        Faro Airport is often the main rental pickup point for Algarve trips and
        southern Portugal driving routes.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Often a practical pickup point for Algarve-focused trips</li>
        <li>Useful for flexible multi-stop itineraries</li>
        <li>Sometimes less necessary for single-resort stays with no driving plans</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Planned page sections</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Pickup and return logistics at Faro Airport</li>
        <li>What travelers should watch for</li>
        <li>Automatic vs manual car availability</li>
        <li>When airport pickup makes sense for your trip</li>
        <li>Common pickup and return issues</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What this page will cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Whether Faro Airport is the right pickup point for your trip</li>
        <li>How airport pickup differs from other rental pickup options</li>
        <li>Which trip types are most likely to benefit from renting here</li>
        <li>What to verify before finalizing a booking</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How this page fits into the site</h2>
      <p>
        This guide will eventually connect to our broader Portugal guide,
        airport rental guides, booking basics, and practical rental guides.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Related Portugal pages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/portugal-guide">Portugal Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/airport-rental-guides">Airport Rental Guides</a></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .top-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card,
    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .side-card a {
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .top-grid,
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>